Wall animals art is decorative wall décor that features animal designs such as deer, horses, lions, birds, elephants, butterflies, or abstract animal shapes. It is used to give a home or office a stylish, natural, and unique look. These pieces are made from materials like metal, wood, resin, canvas, or MDF, and may be flat wall art or 3D mounted designs.

Common Prices of Wall Animals Art (Pakistan)

Prices depend on size, material, and design:

Small pieces: PKR 3,000 – 6,000
Medium pieces: PKR 6,000 – 12,000
Large / premium designs: PKR 12,000+
Where It Is Used
Living room wall
Above sofa
Bedroom wall
TV lounge
Office reception
Hallway / entrance